As we #WearOrange for #NationalGunViolenceAwarenessDay we must offer more than thoughts &amp; prayers for the lives lost to #GunViolence.

@HouseDemocrats have passed common-sense gun legislation &amp; are working on more solutions.

I urge #GOP to join us to save lives &amp; #EndGunViolence https://t.co/uQLFaEHty8

I introduced the Emergency #InfantFormula Act to increase supply amid the shortage crisis. Thanks to @RepDonBacon, my Republican co-lead, for joining to introduce this vital bill.

@SenGillibrand is working to introduce companion legislation in the Senate.
https://t.co/pxtC4FjyJJ

I joined “One World” with @ZainAsher on
 @cnni to discuss the situation in #Ethiopia. We must get food to those who are starving and Eritrea should open its ports to U.N. relief agencies. All parties should agree to a ceasefire. 
https://t.co/R9KnTVdp9q

Join us tonight at 7 PM Pacific for our Telephone Town Hall where we'll discuss our efforts to defeat #COVID19, rebuild our economy and all other issues facing Congress.

We'll be joined by Dr. Lynn Goldman, Dean of the 
@GWpublichealth

Today I spoke with the House Asia Subcommittee and the 
@StateDept's Bureau of East Asian and Pacific Affairs 
@USAsiaPacific regarding the coup in Burma/Myanmar. We currently give $135 million in assistance to Burma/Myanmar.  (1/2)
